data.description: Country living in this multigenerational home with views of the foothills and nature's beauty on 4 plus acres! Inviting covered front porch welcomes as you enter this spacious 5 bedroom, 4 bath property. The kitchen is designed for entertaining with ample cupboard and counter space, stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar, large dining area, and opens to back deck. Master bedroom offers attached bath with dual vanities, soaker tub, walk-in closet and is conveniently located on the main level.  Upper level features bonus living area with built-in desk, 2 bedrooms with built-in bench seats, full bathroom, and plenty of storage. Lower level could be utilized as separate guest quarters with kitchenette, wood-burning stove, washer/dryer hookups, and bathroom. Extra deep 3 car garage with 220V power, 2 water heaters, water softener, and workbench. Lot has room for a garden, animals, RV parking, toys and more! Outdoor recreation abounds! The useable lot space is 3.38 acres, .98 acres is across the road. No CC&Rs!
